data.description: Great opportunity in Slaton to own this cozy home located right by the high school. This is a 3 bedroom home but could use the bonus room as a 4th bedroom or 2nd living area. The kitchen was recently painted (walls & cabinets) and replaced light fixtures in the kitchen, master bathroom and guest bathroom. Spacious living room for entertaining or enjoying a relaxing evening by the fireplace.
